SCOPE OF THIS LICENSE

This repository contains multiple categories of files:

  a) RUNNER FILES (runner/, workers/, wasm/) — governed by this Bitbybit
     Runner License.

  b) COMPANY-OWNED ASSETS (assets/, textures/) — governed by this Bitbybit
     Runner License.

  c) THIRD-PARTY OPEN-SOURCE FILES (babylonjs/, glslang/, twgsl/, havok/,
     fonts/) — governed by their respective licenses (Apache 2.0, MIT,
     ISC, SIL OFL 1.1, LGPL-2.1, zlib, BSD 3-Clause, Havok License).
     See the NOTICE file for a complete list.

  d) MODIFIED FONTS (fonts/) — modified from originals obtained from
     Google Fonts. Governed by their original licenses (SIL Open Font
     License 1.1 or Apache 2.0). Modifications consist of automated
     geometry processing to remove self-intersecting outlines for
     compatibility with 3D text extrusion. See NOTICE for details.

This Bitbybit Runner License applies ONLY to categories (a) and (b) above.
It does not restrict your rights under the third-party licenses that govern
categories (c) and (d).

